1- put the app folder in the dir: "C:\xampp\htdocs" .
2- open app folder in phpstorm or VScode .
3- open mysqlAdmin and create databaas with name: "files" .
4- in terminal run this commands :
       - composer update
       - php artisan migrate
       - php artisan db:seed
       - php artisan key:generate
       - php artisan passport:install  
5- AOP package is installed, for usage example :
https://github.com/AhmadVoid/Laravel-AOP
 